public final class DefaultComparators
extends Object

A collection of default comparator implementations. The following comparators are supported:

  • objectComparator() - a comparator that follows the rules defined for Objects
  • listComparator() - a comparator that follows the rules defined for Lists
  • setComparator() - a comparator that follows the rules defined for Sets
  • mapComparator() - a comparator that follows the rules defined for Maps
Custom comparators can be used by implementing Comparator.
